1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:03,000
A black screen appears with a skull wearing headphones.
Text on screen reads: Use headphones for better experience.

2
00:00:03,000 --> 00:00:12,000
Cut to a dimly lit room.
A young man lies on a bed, holding his phone above his chest.
The room has a cool blue tone, giving a calm but slightly eerie feel.

3
00:00:12,000 --> 00:00:20,000
He continues looking at his phone casually.
Beside him on the bed are small objects, including earphones.
Everything feels normal and quiet.

4
00:00:20,000 --> 00:00:26,000
He gets up and walks toward a door.
As he opens it, a bright yellow light floods in from outside, contrasting the dark room.

5
00:00:26,000 --> 00:00:36,000
He steps into another area and picks up a small object, a box or container.
He examines it under warm lighting.
A strong shadow forms behind him on the wall, adding tension.

6
00:00:36,000 --> 00:00:48,000
He walks toward the door again.
When he opens it, a mysterious person stands outside in darkness, holding a plastic bag.
The visitor’s face is partially hidden, creating suspense.

7
00:00:48,000 --> 00:01:00,000
The man hesitates, then turns and walks back inside.
The room remains dim, with a table lamp glowing in the foreground.
The scene ends with an uneasy atmosphere.

8
00:01:00,000 --> 00:01:08,000
Title card appears: Ninu Veedani Needanu Nene.
Credits roll over a smoky dark background.
